{
  "stem": "2533.5",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] My daughter's name is Marie and she still keeps her maiden name, Zielinski.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know then, but when the museum was starting-- they were building the museum, and when I saw it when it was finished, and I got there for the opening, and then I knew the purpose of my survival.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which is the museum.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To tell the memorial and to tell-- I know it's hundred of us, but every one of us has got different and we've got the same, you know, just to survive, because it's that animal instinct to survive.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when one is young, it's different.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know if I would have survived now or when my mother-- she was only 42, but still.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, when one is young-- I never felt the words-- when my brother said, let's say goodbye, because we won't see, 'til I had my own children-- what it means to be a mother and taking the children to their death.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't easy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's still not easy, but we just have to carry on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Thank you very much for having me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That is the diamond I took out from my great-grandmother's earring, which survived in my lining of my coat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After the war I discovered it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Put it in with other-- my jewelry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we had to give it all up when we were taken to Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that somehow got out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know, it was ripped up, got out, and it got hooked on there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when the jeweler looked at the diamond, he said, that's at least 150 years old.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
